from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score,confusion_matrix,classification_report
def METRICS(y_test,y_pred):
    print("Accuracy Score : " , accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred))
    print("Classification Report: \n" , classification_report(y_test,y_pred))
    print("Confusion Matrix Visualised :",skplot.metrics.plot_confusion_matrix(y_test,y_pred))

from sklearn.metrics import roc_curve
y_pred_prob1 = lr_y_pred
fpr1 , tpr1, thresholds1 = roc_curve(y_test, y_pred_prob1)

y_pred_prob2 = dt_y_pred
fpr2 , tpr2, thresholds2 = roc_curve(y_test, y_pred_prob2)


y_pred_prob3 =bdt_y_pred
fpr3 , tpr3, thresholds3 = roc_curve(y_test, y_pred_prob3)

y_pred_prob4 = b_rfc_y_pred
fpr4 , tpr4, thresholds4 = roc_curve(y_test, y_pred_prob4)


plt.plot([0,1],[0,1], 'k--')
plt.plot(fpr1, tpr1, label= "Logistic Regression")
plt.plot(fpr2, tpr2, label= "Decission Tree")
plt.plot(fpr3, tpr3, label= "Best Decission Tree")
plt.plot(fpr4, tpr4, label= "Best Random Forest")
plt.legend()
plt.xlabel("FPR")
plt.ylabel("TPR")
plt.title('Receiver Operating Characteristic')
plt.show()
